<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Schoolroom</td></tr>
<tr id="L18"><td><a href="#L18">18</a></td><td>KEIKO:  Now, as we discussed in yesterday's lesson, the wormhole was discovered by Commander Sisko and Lieutenant Dax earlier this year. Does anyone know what makes this wormhole so unusual? Jake?</td></tr>

