<tr id="L25"><td><a href="#L25">25</a></td><td>KEIKO:  Yes, on Bajor the entities are worshipped as prophets. Our studies of the wormhole have shown that it was formed by unique particles we call verterons that are apparently self-sustaining in nature. This begins to explain how a ship at impulse can safely pass through</td></tr>

